    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>upside down shallot tart </strong>with the<strong> bacon lardon potatoes</strong> and <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle a little <strong>olive oil </strong>over the salad with the <strong>remaining balsamic vinegar</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
